---
// HeroSection Astro コンポーネント
---

<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center hero-gradient overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute -top-40 -right-40 w-80 h-80 bg-primary-200/30 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-float"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-40 -left-40 w-80 h-80 bg-secondary-200/30 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-float" style="animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container-custom relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="animate-fade-in">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
          外国人研究参加者集め、<br />
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-secondary-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            もう悩まない！
          </span><br />
          <span class="text-3xl md:text-4xl">AIがあなたの研究を加速します</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          研究者が本来の研究活動に集中できるよう、外国人参加者リクルート、研究関連文書の翻訳、関連事務作業を、
          <span class="text-primary-600 font-semibold">AIと専門チームの力で包括的にサポート</span>します。
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center mb-12">
          <button 
            id="contact-btn"
            class="bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 rounded-md"
          >
            まずは無料相談・資料請求
          </button>
          <button 
            id="services-btn"
            class="border-2 border-primary-600 text-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-50 px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 rounded-md"
          >
            サービス詳細を見る
          </button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg animate-slide-in-left">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">15年+</div>
            <div class="text-gray-700">外国人サポート実績</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg animate-slide-in-left" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-secondary-600 mb-2">AI活用</div>
            <div class="text-gray-700">効率的マッチング</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg animate-slide-in-left" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-600 mb-2">24時間</div>
            <div class="text-gray-700">迅速対応体制</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  // スムーススクロール機能
  document.getElementById('contact-btn')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    const element = document.getElementById('contact');
    if (element) {
      element.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
    }
  });

  document.getElementById('services-btn')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    const element = document.getElementById('services');
    if (element) {
      element.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
    }
  });
</script>